HEADWORD: Dissolubility
<hw>Dis`so*lu*bil"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality
of being dissoluble; capacity of being dissoluble; capacity of being
dissolved by heat or moisture, and converted into a fluid.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

